<h2 id="me">About Me</h2>
<p>
  I am a 17-year-old teenager currently living in the Dominican Republic. Born in April 17, 2007,
  I've always had a thing for computers, starting my journey when I was a small 9 year-old which
  was where I found an interest for programming after wondering how YouTube was made.
</p>

<p>
