  and cats are my animal of choice (because I share a lot of personality traits with them :3c).
</p>

<h3 id="projects">My projects</h3>

<p>
  Most of my projects are open-source and related to the community chatting platform,
  <a href="https://revolt.chat/?utm_source=amy">Revolt</a>. I generally focus on frontend development
  as it is the most easy and is where I have the most knowledge on, but I am also learning how to make
